{"tid":2163160,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"而家既連登只可以當笑話睇","createTime":"2020-08-18T13:19:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-09T11:28:58.000Z","uid":10295,"like":8,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"b5af10dc0498d4cfb414ca90b754a77f65791e04","tid":2163160,"uid":10295,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T13:19:52.000Z","msg":"道理唔講啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />齋屌算，唔知幾時開始連登得翻堆弱智小朋友同pr留言，淨係識分化又容易比人帶風向<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />明眼人都知好多post係有人帶風<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />兒登仔難服侍都唔係第一日咖啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />有邊間出名既黃店/出名既手足冇比人屌過<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />其實你地分化完有冇覺得自己係冇思想淨係意氣用事，呢頭踩完人落地底，轉頭又捧到上神枱，其實咁樣買兩邊羞唔羞恥<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />都柒左好多次咖啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />新啲既例子肥佬黎係咁瓏門又係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />一有相反意見就話人五毛分化撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />諗真啲你地同共產黨有咩分別，又會玩埋迫害人果啲招數，要玩到人身敗名裂<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n你地再繼續啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/38.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />繼續咁樣，睇下會點啦，對家而家出曬大絕都唔識團結，個個好似小朋友鬧交咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9845817c043ca08b74d819c2d32436f1e06d732","tid":2163160,"uid":158899,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T13:20:57.000Z","msg":"唔鍾意咪quit lor <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac4d62f5dbcbcc53574e36a642dc7f64635c327e","tid":2163160,"uid":309553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T13:25:09.000Z","msg":"打咁撚多腦魔把撚咩"},{"pid":"892da94cd40a4e161edb18f71c60d4bf3318d8b7","tid":2163160,"uid":10295,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"ac4d62f5dbcbcc53574e36a642dc7f64635c327e","tid":2163160,"uid":309553,"like":0,"